<li>Appearance: gas (colorless), liquid (pale blue)</li>
<li>Group: group 16 (chalcogens)</li>
<li>Block: p-block</li>
<li>Period: period 2</li>
<li>Element category: diatomic nonmetal</li>
<li>Electron configuration: 2s2 2p4</li>
<li>Per shell: 2, 6</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Physical properties</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Phase: gas</li>
<li>Melting point: 54.36 K ​(−218.79 °C, ​−361.82 °F)</li>
<li>Boiling point: 90.188 K ​(−182.962 °C, ​−297.332 °F)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>History</strong></p>
<ul>
